{"tid":1874267,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭敬基呼籲cctvb為員工著想，加強防疫措施","createTime":"2020-02-11T06:12:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T08:28:25.000Z","uid":153600,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"093fcf3f4e1dc87ec9e5bf7b36ec5eb94d54a3c6","tid":1874267,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T06:12:38.000Z","msg":"盧苑茵同鄭敬基曾經喺《卡拉屋企》演母子，今日鄭敬基喺網上透露，知道 Madam Lo 今日要番 TVB 試造型，不過已經用晒屋企啲口罩。Madam Lo 唯有戴住卡通棉布口罩，入面夾一格廁紙，外面再包保鮮紙就番 TVB 開工，好慘！<br />\n<br />\n鄭敬基話聽到好心痛，馬上拎咗四十幾個口罩出去比 Madam Lo 同囡囡，罷搭地鐵嘅佢仲為 Madam Lo 破例約喺地鐵交收。<br />\n<br />\n一見面鄭敬基就即刻幫佢戴口罩，仲話睇到好心酸，諗起呢個就係香港好多人面對緊嘅問題，亦指 TVB「堂堂一間上市公司，竟然沒有每日起碼提供一個口罩給所有員工。無怪乎給黃（王）維基先生一間沒有電視製作的HKTV，市值過了有電視工廠美譽嘅TVB，多諷刺。」<br />\n<br />\n鄭敬基叫開緊工嘅演員們多啲關心一班前輩演員，因為佢地難為情唔敢開口問，亦懇請 TVB 提供口罩同加強防疫措施。"},{"pid":"9bc560e13d6fe7221b4d885535e05639f1dfb1c6","tid":1874267,"uid":3405,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T06:18:36.000Z","msg":"黃到痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反佢條垃圾徒弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab92a8518a1e010ef56cbb166c7b40b2dd39fa57","tid":1874267,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T07:50:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6c16427da3b550e953ef90b961ce1e94322bbf0","tid":1874267,"uid":78072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bc560e13d6fe7221b4d885535e05639f1dfb1c6","tid":1874267,"uid":3405,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T06:18:36.000Z","msg":"黃到痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反佢條垃圾徒弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T08:15:56.000Z","msg":"佢徒弟邊位?"},{"pid":"aef82b67bec924f44da0870156fc5a315152